#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click Here To Watch More Episodes Of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:

'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Dhyan Sreenivasan takes the hot seat as the host of Son of Sreenivasan Roast, where he gets hilariously grilled alongside his guests‚ÄîNeeraj Madhav, Aju Varghese, and Vishnu Raghav. Expect witty comebacks, savage burns, and non-stop laughter as they dish out jokes, share behind-the-scenes fun, and promote their upcoming web series Love Under Construction, streaming on JioHotstar from February 28.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4331 - Bhide ke Surprise se Ude Gada Family ke Hosh?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Bhide Ka Surprise | Bhide dega Jhatka | Gokuldham Society

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Judwaa - Episode 20 - 25th Feb 2025 [ Aina Asif & Adnan Raza Mir ] - HUM TV

Judwaa is the story of twin girls who share the same face but have contrasting personalities and destinies. One is gentle and reserved, while the other is bold and fearless. As fate weaves unexpected twists, their lives take dramatic turns. Starring Aina Asif in a dual role, this gripping drama explores identity, destiny, and the power of choice.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: When You Have a Crush On Your Boss - Part 2| Ft. Keshav Sadhna,  Anjum Khan, Reshham Sahaani
snippet.description:
#filtercopy #officeromace #crush

Kaisa laga Part 2? Comments mein batao üòã

Ever felt that sudden wave of... something... when your boss is around? We're diving into that feeling! Yeah, we've all been there! In this super fun video, we're diving straight into the hilarious mess of having a crush on your boss! üòÖ

We've packed it with all the relatable moments of office romance, the kind where you're constantly wondering, "Is this real, or am I just imagining things?" ü§∑‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è From accidental touches during team meetings to trying to decipher those "friendly" smiles that might mean something more, every moment is a minefield of mixed signals.You know that feeling when you're trying to act cool, but your heart is doing a bhangra inside? 

This video is for anyone who's ever had a crush on their boss, found themselves overthinking every little interaction, or just loves a good dose of desi comedy. Get ready for some serious LOL moments, a few cringes (because, let's be honest, we've all been there!), and a whole lot of "OMG, same!" vibes.

So settle in, and get ready to dive into the chaos of office romance. Don't forget to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE for more hilarious content! And share your own office crush stories in the comments ‚Äì we want to hear all the juicy details! üòâ Let's see if your office crush stories are as crazy as ours!

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Amit and Darshana‚Äîtwo colleagues, two friends, and a bond that feels effortless. From shared coffee breaks to deep conversations, they understand each other in ways no one else does. In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started from February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. After the victory against Bangladesh, Team India also won against Pakistan by 6 wickets. While there is a wave of happiness among Indian cricket fans, Pakistani cricket fans are afraid that Pakistan is almost out of the Champions Trophy. How excited are Pakistani fans for the India vs Pakistan match? Virat Kohli became the hero of victory for India who scored a brilliant century. Why did the fans of the Pakistan cricket team become admirers of the Indian cricket team? Why did the Pakistan cricket fans get angry at the star players of the Pakistani team Babar Azam, Haris Rauf, Shaheen Afridi, Mohammad Rizwan? Why did the much-discussed Pakistani bowling fail in front of Shubman Gill, Shreyas Iyer, Virat, Rohit Sharma? What happened when after the India vs Pakistan match in Dubai, Indian cricket fans and Pakistani cricket fans together trolled and roasted the Pakistan cricket team. To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch.

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started from February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. After the victory against Bangladesh, Team India also won against Pakistan by 6 wickets. While there is a wave of happiness among Indian cricket fans, Pakistani cricket fans are afraid that Pakistan is almost out of the Champions Trophy. How excited are Pakistani fans for the India vs Pakistan match? Virat Kohli became the hero of victory for India who scored a brilliant century. Why did the fans of the Pakistan cricket team become admirers of the Indian cricket team? Why did the Pakistan cricket fans get angry at the star players of the Pakistani team Babar Azam, Haris Rauf, Shaheen Afridi, Mohammad Rizwan? Why did the much-discussed Pakistani bowling fail in front of Shubman Gill, Shreyas Iyer, Virat, Rohit Sharma? What happened when after the India vs Pakistan match in Dubai, Indian cricket fans and Pakistani cricket fans together trolled and roasted the Pakistan cricket team. To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch.

Bajjo Episode 65 - [Eng Sub] - Javeria Saud - Arez Ahmed - Suqaynah Khan - 26th February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Bajjo is a heartfelt family drama that blends light-hearted moments with emotional turbulence. It portrays the struggles and conflicts of a middle-class household, where differences and arguments often take center stage.
Musarrat, fondly called Bajjo, is the eldest sibling, known for her sharp tongue and bitter demeanor. Her unmarried status fuels her frustration, leading to threats of drastic actions if anyone weds before her. This turmoil unsettles the entire family, but when a proposal finally comes her way, it brings its own set of challenges.
Will Bajjo ever find her match? Can her attitude change, or will it continue to cause problems for her family? Is her family‚Äôs patience running out, or will they stand by her despite her flaws? Can Bajjo overcome her struggles?
